<p id="fs-id1163721451483">Compute <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline"><semantics><mrow><mrow><msub><mi>x</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></mrow></mrow><annotation-xml encoding="MathML-Content"><mrow><msub><mi>x</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></mrow></annotation-xml></semantics></math> and <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline"><semantics><mrow><mrow><msub><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></mrow></mrow><annotation-xml encoding="MathML-Content"><mrow><msub><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></mrow></annotation-xml></semantics></math> using the specified iterative method.</p>
