<div data-type="exercise" id="fs-id1165043251688">
<div data-type="problem" id="fs-id1165043251691">
<p id="fs-id1165043251693"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline"><semantics><mrow><mrow><mi>f</mi><mrow><mo>(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>,</mo><msub><mi>x</mi><mn>0</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></mrow><annotation-xml encoding="MathML-Content"><mrow><mi>f</mi><mrow><mo>(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>,</mo><msub><mi>x</mi><mn>0</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></annotation-xml></semantics></math></p>
</div>
<div data-type="solution" id="fs-id1165042473412">
<p id="fs-id1165042473414">Newton: <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline"><semantics><mrow><mrow><mn>11</mn></mrow></mrow><annotation-xml encoding="MathML-Content"><mrow><mn>11</mn></mrow></annotation-xml></semantics></math> iterations, secant: <math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline"><semantics><mrow><mrow><mn>16</mn></mrow></mrow><annotation-xml encoding="MathML-Content"><mrow><mn>16</mn></mrow></annotation-xml></semantics></math> iterations</p>
</div>
</div>
<div data-type="exercise" id="fs-id1165042645634">
<div data-type="problem" id="fs-id1165042645637">
<p id="fs-id1165042645639"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline"><semantics><mrow><mrow><mi>f</mi><mrow><mo>(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>,</mo><msub><mi>x</mi><mn>0</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></mrow><annotation-xml encoding="MathML-Content"><mrow><mi>f</mi><mrow><mo>(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>,</mo><msub><mi>x</mi><mn>0</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></annotation-xml></semantics></math></p>
